{"tid":2284250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協申請11月15日集會及遊行 獲發反對通知書 記協提出上訴","createTime":"2020-11-13T06:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T10:06:36.000Z","uid":292499,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7198eca6ac16107b8065a0ea1beb509cdcbea3e8","tid":2284250,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"記協表示，計劃在 11 月 15 日在港島舉行業界集會及遊行，抗議警方濫捕記者，並要求在查冊機制中加入傳媒選項，但有關申請遭警方發出反對通知書。記協已就此提出上訴，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會今日下午 3 時將舉行聆訊，記協副主席陳朗昇及執委會成員將出席聆訊，聆訊前將會見傳媒，講解上訴理據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/記協擬-11-15-遊行撐被捕港台編導-警發反對通知書-記協已上訴今午聆訊/?fbclid=IwAR1SDEOAY0kXUx8qoIzv0zuPQy603rnYESH_3TE8mw6Uh9IK7DkSypOJqbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E6%93%AC-11-15-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%92%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E7%B7%A8%E5%B0%8E-%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BC%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E5%B7%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E4%BB%8A%E5%8D%88%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SDEOAY0kXUx8qoIzv0zuPQy603rnYESH_3TE8mw6Uh9IK7DkSypOJqbs&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=2f1b2f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E6%93%AC-11-15-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%92%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E7%B7%A8%E5%B0%8E-%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BC%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E5%B7%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E4%BB%8A%E5%8D%88%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1SDEOAY0kXUx8qoIzv0zuPQy603rnYESH_3TE8mw6Uh9IK7DkSypOJqbs&h=52307d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/記協擬-11-15-遊行撐被捕港台編導-警發反對通知書-記協已上訴今午聆訊/?fbclid=IwAR1SDEOAY0kXUx8qoIzv0zuPQy603rnYESH_3TE8mw6Uh9IK7DkSypOJqbs</a>"},{"pid":"a8d43f25c9cd0032cc86e27398466b5fdd8c5ec6","tid":2284250,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"DOJ準備介入去駁回上訴申